description: Be transported to Morocco with this delicious chicken tagine dish bursting with bold flavours from cumin, garlic, coriander and dates.
name: Moroccan Chicken Tagine Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: When ready to serve, place couscous in a heatproof bowl. Add 1 cup boiling water and remaining oil. Stir well. Cover and set aside for 5 minutes or until absorbed. Fluff with a fork. Spoon couscous onto plates and top with chicken and vegetables. Garnish with pistachios and coriander sprigs.
